headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid TECH and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Bio-Techne’s 21% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 10.9%, and its stock price has climbed to $62.36 per share. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
